<HEADLINE>
<P>
GOVERNMENT-RUN BROTHEL PROMISED NICE TURNABOUT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Regarding "Mustang Ranch Seized," (Sept. 20), I was very excited when the 
federal government took over operation of the infamous Mustang Ranch (a 
105-room brothel in Nevada now being liquidated by the IRS). 
</P>
<P>
I was equally disturbed when they changed their mind. It would have been the 
first time in history that the people could do to the government what the 
government has been doing to them all these years. 
</P>
<P>
DARRYL O. DICKEY 
</P>
<P>
Reseda 
</P>
