SHOOTINGS -- ISRAEL; PALESTINIANS -- ISRAEL; ISRAEL -- REVOLTS; UNITED NATIONS 
-- PLO; BUSH, GEORGE; ISRAEL -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- PLO; UNITED NATIONS -- 
