DEMONSTRATIONS -- SOUTH KOREA; ESPIONAGE -- SOUTH KOREA; CIVIL RIGHTS 
VIOLATIONS; HUNGER STRIKES; KIM DAE JUNG; ROH TAE WOO 
</P>
