</P>
<P>
D'OYLY CARTE -- THE COMPANY THAT ONCE DEFINED LIGHT OPERA -- IS ATTEMPTING TO 
RE-ESTABLISH ITS PROMINENCE ON STAGED'OYLY CARTE -- THE COMPANY THAT ONCE 
DEFINED LIGHT OPERA -- IS ATTEMPTING TO RE-ESTABLISH ITS PROMINENCE ON 
STAGED'OYLY CARTE OPERA COMPANYFESTIVAL OF BRITAIN ORANGE COUNTY 1990ENGLAND -- 
CULTUREOPERA 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By CHRIS PASLES 
</P>
