</P>
<P>
The district: Marina del Rey, Playa del Rey, Westchester, Culver City, Ladera 
Heights, Baldwin Hills, and the Crenshaw area. 
</P>
<P>
Candidate: Gwen Moore (inc.) 
</P>
<P>
